OL,6,FAn environmental pressure group has
OL,7,Fbrought a rare legal action against the
OL,8,Ffinancial regulator, the Financial
OL,9,FConduct Authority (FCA).
OL,11,FIt is the latest in a series of
OL,12,Finnovative legal challenges brought by
OL,13,Fthe legal campaign group ClientEarth.
OL,15,FThe group has brought actions against
OL,16,Fthe directors of Shell, the European
OL,17,FCommission, French bank BNP Paribas,
OL,18,Fand food conglomerate Danone in a bid
OL,19,Fto force corporations and regulators to
OL,20,Fimprove responses to the climate change
OL,21,Fthreat.
OL,3,CFossil fuel risks prompts rare legal
OL,4,Cthreats to North Sea oil and gas fields
